.TH CBT-RUN-PHASES "1" "February 2026" "cbt-run-phases (cbt) 0.1" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
cbt-run-phases \- run script phases
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cbt-run-phases
\fI--global-config CONFIG --script SCRIPTS \fR[\fIPHASES_VARNAME\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Loads the given global and script configurations and executes the phases defined
in them.
.PP
By default, it executes the phases defined in the $phases environment variable,
but it is also possible to specify another environment variable.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-global\-config\fR
Bash script containing global configuration settings
.TP
\fB\-\-script\fR
Bash script containing a script configuration
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Display help page
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Display version
